WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:04.271
Good morning, family. How have you all been doing? I hope you're doing well.

00:00:04.272 --> 00:00:11.754
I have some things on my heart to tell you. First, I'm going to tell you what the Lord is talking to me about: a diet.

00:00:11.755 --> 00:00:18.891
A lot of people are asking how I'm losing weight, and it's just what the Holy Spirit has been talking to me about.

00:00:18.892 --> 00:00:29.786
He said to me that for the days that are coming—he even brought it up in my dreams last night—there is a plague coming.

00:00:29.787 --> 00:01:02.739
He said, 'Brandon, there is a plague, another massive wave.'The first wave was COVID from 2020 until 2022, and it receded, but he said there will be a day soon when there will be another plague, and this one will dwarf COVID.

00:01:02.740 --> 00:01:26.427
A lot of people will perish because of this. He said, 'I want you to tell my people that it's time for them to take their health more seriously.'They need to start exercising, even just walking.

00:01:26.428 --> 00:01:47.438
Exercise is important for getting your blood flowing and taking care of your bodies. It needs to become a lifestyle habit.

00:01:47.439 --> 00:02:06.810
The Lord said it doesn't have to be a long time, just 30 minutes a day or every other day, but start keeping your body moving.

00:02:06.811 --> 00:02:44.635
I asked the Lord for a lifestyle to maintain weight, and he instructed me to go on a Whole Foods diet: beef, chicken, fish, vegetables, fruit, and eggs.

00:02:44.636 --> 00:02:59.461
He said if you read a label at the market and can't pronounce half the ingredients, do not put it in your body.

00:02:59.462 --> 00:03:08.640
He said, 'Brandon, they are poisoning you, and you don't even know it.'My people perish for a lack of knowledge.

00:03:08.641 --> 00:03:25.587
If you are not studying and don't know what's on that label, do not consume it.

00:03:25.588 --> 00:03:43.685
Eat things that do not have a nutrition label; fish is fish, and chicken is chicken. Stay with Whole Foods.

00:03:43.686 --> 00:04:10.019
Then he talked to me about supplements and how many companies are not good; they are in it for profit and use unhealthy ingredients.

00:04:10.020 --> 00:04:12.929
My wife is very educated and is looking up trustworthy companies.

00:04:12.930 --> 00:05:09.518
I used to take all kinds of vitamins, but the Lord told me to stop because I didn't know what they were putting in them.

00:05:09.519 --> 00:05:35.190
Study the brand of vitamin you are taking and who is making it.

00:05:35.191 --> 00:05:44.999
There are many different opinions, so you have to follow the Holy Spirit for your own life.

00:05:45.000 --> 00:06:12.113
I believe if you keep it under 1,500 calories and exercise, you'll drop weight. I'm learning that my body doesn't need as much as it used to.

00:06:12.114 --> 00:06:23.541
You don't have to snack all the time; you can intermittent fast and take care of your body.

00:06:23.542 --> 00:06:38.299
It doesn't have to be an addiction to food. I was codependent on junk, but I am determined to live long and finish strong.

00:06:38.300 --> 00:07:07.476
Secondly, the Lord spoke to me about the youth. They are looking for an authentic move of the Spirit. They are hungry for the supernatural.

00:07:07.477 --> 00:07:32.031
He said there's been a lot of charismatic flakiness and fleshly behavior in churches, which is a turn-off for them.

00:07:32.032 --> 00:07:45.970
What's coming next will be a weight of the tangible presence of my Shekinah Glory.

00:07:45.971 --> 00:07:55.471
The presence of the Lord will come into the atmosphere of the church to the point where it affects the whole congregation.

00:07:55.472 --> 00:08:33.342
There will be no mistaking it or mocking it. You will feel the weight of the tangible presence of God so strongly that there will be a holy hush upon the congregation.

00:08:33.343 --> 00:08:50.829
You won't want to move because the fear of the Lord is tangible in that building.

00:08:50.830 --> 00:09:09.490
There is a holy reverence where you just want to sit and weep before the presence and the power of the Lord.

00:09:09.491 --> 00:09:39.451
The Lord told me there will be a move of his Spirit in churches that feels like a weight on the people, including the children. I'm so excited this is coming.

00:09:39.452 --> 00:10:06.119
He said, 'I will have the harvest of souls from this generation like this world has never seen before.'They are searching for a move of something to help their depression and anxiety.

00:10:06.120 --> 00:11:10.359
He also talked about Europe. Over a year ago, I saw soldiers in a single file line going toward Europe.

00:11:10.360 --> 00:11:32.040
It was a major draft. The Lord showed me that the war had escalated into a World War III scenario.

00:11:32.041 --> 00:11:40.979
I heard that the great Apollyon is being released upon the Earth.

00:11:40.980 --> 00:11:51.474
I saw a massive, demonic-looking angelic being—a huge principality—come out of the ocean.

00:11:51.475 --> 00:13:00.661
I saw a demon chained in a pit, and an angelic being from the Lord came down and released that spirit.

00:13:00.662 --> 00:13:43.518
It looked like it was wearing a fur Viking outfit with thick white hair and a horned helmet. Its face was vicious.

00:13:43.519 --> 00:14:09.717
It started spinning like the Tasmanian Devil and went inside Vladimir Putin, as if he became possessed.

00:14:09.718 --> 00:14:27.952
All of a sudden, I saw him strike Poland because Poland was provoking Russia.

00:14:27.953 --> 00:14:50.106
Near the Warsaw and Belarus area, I saw a humongous mushroom cloud explosion.

00:14:50.107 --> 00:15:36.559
I thought they were tactical nukes, but the Lord said, 'No, this is a weapon that has never been used before.'It vaporized everything in a huge radius.

00:15:36.560 --> 00:16:10.600
When this happened, World War III escalated even more. Turkey joined in with Russia, funding them and beating ancient drums.

00:16:10.601 --> 00:16:49.946
Then Iran joined them, and they came against Israel. I saw men with red hats marching toward Israel.

00:16:49.947 --> 00:17:04.441
The Lord told me this is the beginning of the Ezekiel 38 and 39 war—Gog and Magog.

00:17:04.442 --> 00:17:14.479
The United States did not participate because we were busy with Europe.

00:17:14.480 --> 00:17:55.194
People called it 'the Great Betrayal'because we did not help Israel.

00:17:55.195 --> 00:18:28.879
I saw China shoot something that looked like a red dragon over America. I saw a surprise attack on Hawaii, similar to Pearl Harbor.

00:18:28.880 --> 00:19:17.518
Honolulu and the Big Island were at war with China, and they were bombing the people with F-16s.

00:19:17.519 --> 00:19:30.633
Fast forward to today: none of this was happening two years ago.

00:19:30.634 --> 00:20:11.429
Now we hear about the Prime Minister of France talking about nuclear weapons within NATO, and Putin saying this would be the beginning of World War III.

00:20:11.430 --> 00:20:45.367
We are seeing the escalation against Iran. In 2022, an angel told me in a dream that great judgment would begin 569 days from that day.

00:20:45.368 --> 00:21:38.650
That math pointed to October 2nd, and then Israel was attacked on October 7th, 2023.

00:21:38.651 --> 00:22:31.827
I warned everyone to watch August 24th, 2023, which was when Saudi Arabia joined the BRICS nations.

00:22:31.828 --> 00:24:29.273
The Lord brought up the dollar again last night. He said the purchasing power of the dollar will be around 50 cents.

00:24:29.274 --> 00:24:38.549
He said there will be a major event that causes a significant stock market crash, similar to 1930.

00:24:38.550 --> 00:25:23.897
He said it's coming. I told you all to watch the mulberry tree at wintertime and to stay on the back of your rug.

00:25:23.898 --> 00:25:36.655
It's fixing to happen in Poland—in the Warsaw and Belarus area.

00:25:36.656 --> 00:25:58.897
God protect those people. We know these things must happen because they are biblical.

00:25:58.898 --> 00:26:15.710
Regarding the plague and the 'pale'horse, it's part of the end times.

00:26:15.711 --> 00:27:42.975
The Lord is coming back for a glorious church that is on fire and victorious. There is a mighty move of God about to happen.

00:27:42.976 --> 00:28:44.875
A supernatural event is about to take place with finances where the wealth of the sinner is laid up for the just.

00:28:44.876 --> 00:29:01.457
Father, we thank you for every person represented here. We call their unsaved loved ones into the kingdom of God.

00:29:01.458 --> 00:29:55.903
We break the bondage of darkness and call them to be flooded with light. Raise up new Davids, Daniels, and Joshuas.

00:29:55.904 --> 00:33:34.879
We call for healing over every person: those with high blood sugar, diabetes, or heart disease.

00:33:34.880 --> 00:34:17.610
We call for new kidneys, hearts, and livers. We curse cancer and Alzheimer's.

00:34:17.611 --> 00:35:10.895
We call for healing over stomach viruses and thyroid issues.

00:35:10.896 --> 00:35:53.683
We bless every person who supports this channel. We are going from glory to glory in the name of Jesus. Amen.

